Sporting club director Augusto Ignacio said: 'It’s not like the old days when players left Sporting at any price.

'The termination clause ensures a great deal for Sporting. I am very pleased with the negotiations.' 

Meanwhile, United have also been credited with interest in Fiorentina's Juan Cuadrado and Juventus midfielder Arturo Vidal.

